{"tid":2513054,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"香港即日極限遊船河","createTime":"2021-05-02T08:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T08:19:01.000Z","uid":294238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5c2d305e41bd1b2cc453a973339d1272ae1abba1","tid":2513054,"uid":294238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T08:15:22.000Z","msg":"條件<br />\n1. 去盡量多碼頭而唔重覆<br />\n2. 只揀持牌/專營渡輪或街渡<br />\n3. 只參考平日正常班次<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRxMKxtdeUFxW7srNEv9PQwkTK4GSjpcAp358gKbTKVFt?filename=ay31NED.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fay31NED.png&h=37626991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n極限玩法就係早一晚去東龍洲露營<br />\n晨早就由08:50東龍洲搭頭班船<br />\n一路由三家村跳碼頭去到長洲<br />\n<br />\n長洲等船比較耐<br />\n所以食個靚晏再去芝麻灣<br />\n(長洲-芝麻灣-梅窩係一程船，唔落船)<br />\n一路去到坪洲再轉港外線去喜靈洲<br />\n總共搭船經過13個碼頭<br />\n<br />\n最後當然要搭返船返坪洲<br />\n再轉船返中環<br />\n全日成人船費計落只需$148咋喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c5c19670351dbe079fd9cb0d66e6f2188cb997","tid":2513054,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T08:19:01.000Z","msg":"係坪洲食埋雞翼陳先走啦喂"}]}